high_descs: Turn left and head to the kitchen countertop.
Pick up the cup on the right from the counter.
Turn left to reach the sink.
Wash the cup in the sink and take it out.
Turn left to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the cup on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed cup on the sink.

high_descs: Turn round the Right side on the countertop.
Take on the bowl in washing sink.
Then put the cup in the water.
Then take the sink on the other side.
Put the cup in the sink on the other side.
anns.task_desc: Clearing the cup then take it from the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the counter top.
Take the cup from the counter top.
Turn around go near the sink.
Put the cup into the sink and washed it.
Take it out and go near the sink.
Put the cup on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Placed the cup on the sink.
